---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-[#F8FAFC] border-t border-slate-100 px-6 py-20 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
          <div class="h-6 w-6 rounded bg-[#0EA5E9] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#0F172A] uppercase">
            Lux<span class="text-[#0EA5E9]">Clinique</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
          Excelência em medicina estética e bem-estar. Protocolos exclusivos com tecnologia de ponta para resultados naturais e seguros.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900 mb-6">Tratamentos</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
          <li>Preenchimento Facial</li>
          <li>Bioestimuladores</li>
          <li>Laser & Peeling</li>
          <li>Lipo Sem Cortes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900 mb-6">Institucional</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
          <li>Corpo Clínico</li>
          <li>Tecnologias</li>
          <li>Política de Privacidade</li>
          <li>Responsabilidade Médica</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900 mb-6">Unidades</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
          <li>Av. Brigadeiro Faria Lima, 3477</li>
          <li>Itaim Bibi, São Paulo - SP</li>
          <li>RT: Dra. Ana Silva - CRM 123456</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-slate-200 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-6 sm:flex-row">
      <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-bold">
        © {currentYear} Lux Clinique. Todos os direitos reservados.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="#" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-[#0EA5E9] transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
